com.scvngr.levelup.core.model

Class Interstitial

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.scvngr.levelup.core.model.Interstitial
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parcelable

    @Immutable
@LevelUpApi(contract=INTERNAL)
public final class Interstitial
extends Object
implements Parcelable
    Model representing a receipt interstitial. An interstitial is a callout that is shown on a receipt which offers a call to action to the user. The call to action can be to claim more credit at a merchant, invite their friends to try the merchant, or some other type.
